window.bookSummaryJSON = "From the author of the award-winning <i>Ender's Game</i> comes the unforgettable story of young Alvin Maker, the seventh son of a seventh son. <p>Born into an alternative frontier America, where life is hard and folk magic is real, Alvin is gifted with power, but he must learn to use his gift wisely. Dark forces are arrayed against Alvin, and only a young girl with second sight can protect him.</p>"; 
